        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/2/2/1",
        "text": [
          ": سمعته يقول: ما من شئ إلا وفيه كتاب أو سنة"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.ammaar-muslim": [
            "1. [1/-] al-Kafi: Ali from Muhammad b. Isa from Yunus from Hammad from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام, he (Hammad) said: I heard him saying: there is nothing except there is about it [a ruling in the] Book or Sunna."
          ]
        }
